## Overview

| cfl:noheader | Description |
| --- | --- |
| **Trigger** | User confirms account deletion. |
| **Actors** | User<br>System |
| **Preconditions** | Valid access token is provided<br>User (ref:EN0005) exists |
| **Postconditions** | User is permanently removed<br>Associated LessonProgress (ref:EN0006) is removed<br>Session is invalidated |

## Main Flow

1. *User:* confirms account deletion  
2. *System:* validates access token  
3. *System:* deletes User (ref:EN0005)  
4. *System:* cascade deletes associated LessonProgress (ref:EN0006)  
5. *System:* invalidates session  
6. *System:* confirms deletion  
End

## 2A: Invalid Access Token

- *System:* rejects request  
End

## 3A: User Not Found

- *System:* rejects request  
End

## Related Entities

- ref:EN0005 – User  
- ref:EN0006 – LessonProgress  

## Related Services

- ref:SRV0003 – UserService  
- ref:SRV0007 – SessionService  

## Notes on Implementation Constraints

- Deletion is irreversible  
- Session must not remain valid after deletion  
- Deterministic training core must remain unaffected  
